steps.name: Input login fleet on login page.
Input password fleet on login page
Login button press.
Choose user type Fleet on Login Page.
Click on the button "Create at least one Driver Account"
Open page add truck.
Enter the name of the test driver
Enter the lastname of the test driver
Enter the license number of the test driver
Choosing the driver's home terminal zone
Choosing the USA driver's working cycle
Choosing the CAN driver's working cycle
Turning on the Yard Move function for the driver
Turning on the Personal Convenience function for the driver
Enter login driver's test
Enter password driver's test
Enter confirm password driver's test
Click on the save driver button
Confirm adding a driver
Back to main Fleet page from Drivers Page.
Open main menu on Fleet Account.
Open the Drivers page in the Fleet manager menu
Back to main Fleet page from Drivers Page.
Open main menu on Fleet Account.
Open the Drivers page in the Fleet manager menu
Click on the driver search icon in the list.
Enter the driver's name in the search.
Back to main menu.
Back to main Fleet page from Drivers Page.
Логинимся на Веб под админкой (5:test)
Click to Button "Create at least one Truck record"
Confirm displayed message about empty trucklist.
Open page add truck.
Input truck number.
Input ELD Device number.
Input wrong VIN Number truck.
Input license plate truck.
Input make truck.
Input Model Truck.
Input Model Year.
Choose fuel type.
Choose Methanol fuel type.
Click to save truck button.
Check alert about wrong VIN Number truck.
